        "management": "Pulse methylprednisolone 500-1000 mg IV x 3 days. Increase maintenance immunosuppression (tacrolimus, MMF, prednisolone). Steroid-resistant: T-cell depleting agents (anti-thymocyte globulin ATG 1.5 mg/kg x 3-5 days). Check DSA for concurrent AMR. Optimize tacrolimus trough (8-12 ng/mL)."
