        "management": "Pulse steroids. IVIG (2 g/kg over 2-4 days). Plasmapheresis (5-7 sessions). Rituximab 375 mg/m2 x 1. Bortezomib for plasma cell depletion. Eculizumab for complement-mediated AMR. Optimize maintenance immunosuppression. Remove DSA."
