          { "feature": "proteinuria", "weight": 4 },
          { "feature": "hypertension", "weight": 3 },
          { "feature": "chronic_ifta_on_biopsy", "weight": 5 }
        ],
        "management": "Prevent progression: optimize BP (ACEi/ARB), reduce proteinuria, maintain adequate immunosuppression (avoid minimization). Treat concurrent AMR if DSA+ (IVIG, rituximab). No specific therapy to reverse established IFTA. Prepare for dialysis or retransplant."
